id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104med1665702536765.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/med1665702536765.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/med1665702536765.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"med1665702536765\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Returns the properties of this Uniface data object.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"med1665702536765__topic_d127991e1_d127992e1_d127993e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"med1665702536765__p_d127994e1_d127995e1_d127996e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Return</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Object</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">.<span class=\"keyword apiname\">getProperties()</span>\n</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"med1665702536765__section_w1869ab1b5b3_w1870ab1b5_w1871ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d208362e70\">Arguments </h2>\n<p class=\"p\">None</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"med1665702536765__section_w1872ab1b5b5_w1873ab1b5_w1874ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d208362e79\">Return Value</h2>\n<dl class=\"dl parml\" id=\"med1665702536765__parml_jr5_wq3_dwb\">\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\">Return</dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">A JavaScript object with each attribute representing a field, occurrence, or component\n            property. For example, in JavaScript Object Notation (JSON), such an object is\n            represented as:<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104med1665702536765_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"med1665702536765__codeblock_tjc_zq3_dwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">{\n \"style:color\" : \"red\",\n \"html:title\" : \"incorrect value\"\n}</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div></dd>\n</dl>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"med1665702536765__section_w1875ab1b5b7_w1876ab1b5_w1877ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d208362e99\">Exceptions</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The following exceptions may be thrown:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">uniface.InvalidDataObjectException</code></li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"med1665702536765__section_uyd_szw_1dc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d208362e116\">Example: Setting and Copying a Group of Properties </h2>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104med1665702536765_html_1\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"med1665702536765__codeblock_v4r_br3_dwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">webtrigger\nscope\n input\n output\nendscope\njavascript\n var DSPInstance = uniface.getInstance();\n var vEnt = DSPInstance.getEntity(\"ENTITY_A.MY\");\n var vOcc = vEnt.getOccurrence(0); \n var vSource = vOcc.getField(\"SOURCE.ENTITY_A.MY\");\n var vTarget = vOcc.getField(\"TARGET.ENTITY_A.MY\");\n// setting properties\n vSource.setProperties({\"html:class\":\"form-control input-sm\",\"style:color\":\"black\",\"backcolor\":\"pink\"});\n//copy properties\n vTarget.setProperties(vSource.getProperties());\nendjavascript\nend</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/shk1665703139073.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uniface.InvalidDataObjectException</a><p>Exception thrown if the object on which the function is called is no longer valid.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/sno1665702583691.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Widgets for Dynamic Server Pages</a><p>Widget definitions for Dynamic Server Pages (DSPs) are used to generate the HTML elements and controls used to represent fields, labels, occurrences, and entities displayed in the client browser.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fql1665702536920.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>clearProperties()</a><p>Restores the initial widget properties of the Uniface data object.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hwh1665702536527.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>getProperty()</a><p>Returns the value of a property of this Uniface data object.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qbz1665702536840.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>setProperties()</a><p>Sets widget properties for a Uniface data object in JavaScript.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/reb1665702537007.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uniface.Entity</a><p>The uniface.Entity object provides access to selected properties of the component entity that it represents. It is returned by the getEntities and getEntity functions of the uniface.Instance and uniface.Occurrence objects.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hfh1665702535808.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uniface.Occurrence</a><p>The uniface.Occurrence object provides access to selected properties of the occurrence that it represents. It is returned by the getOccurrence function of the uniface.Entity object.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dlx1665702535259.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uniface.Field</a><p>The uniface.Field object provides access to selected properties of the field that it represents. It is returned by the getField function of uniface.Occurrence.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529874\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529874\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "getProperties() Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Feb 25, 2026 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Returns the properties of this Uniface data object. Return = Object . getProperties() Arguments None Return Value Return A JavaScript object with each attribute representing a field, occurrence, or component property. For example, in JavaScript Object Notation (JSON), such an object is represented as: Explain this code { \"style:color\" : \"red\", \"html:title\" : \"incorrect value\" } Copy Exceptions The following exceptions may be thrown: uniface.InvalidDataObjectException Example: Setting and Copying a Group of Properties Explain this code webtrigger scope input output endscope javascript var DSPInstance = uniface.getInstance(); var vEnt = DSPInstance.getEntity(\"ENTITY_A.MY\"); var vOcc = vEnt.getOccurrence(0); var vSource = vOcc.getField(\"SOURCE.ENTITY_A.MY\"); var vTarget = vOcc.getField(\"TARGET.ENTITY_A.MY\"); // setting properties vSource.setProperties({\"html:class\":\"form-control input-sm\",\"style:color\":\"black\",\"backcolor\":\"pink\"}); //copy properties vTarget.setProperties(vSource.getProperties()); endjavascript end Copy Related Links uniface.InvalidDataObjectException Exception thrown if the object on which the function is called is no longer valid. Widgets for Dynamic Server Pages Widget definitions for Dynamic Server Pages (DSPs) are used to generate the HTML elements and controls used to represent fields, labels, occurrences, and entities displayed in the client browser. clearProperties() Restores the initial widget properties of the Uniface data object. getProperty() Returns the value of a property of this Uniface data object. setProperties() Sets widget properties for a Uniface data object in JavaScript. uniface.Entity The uniface.Entity object provides access to selected properties of the component entity that it represents. It is returned by the getEntities and getEntity functions of the uniface.Instance and uniface.Occurrence objects. uniface.Occurrence The uniface.Occurrence object provides access to selected properties of the occurrence that it represents. It is returned by the getOccurrence function of the uniface.Entity object. uniface.Field The uniface.Field object provides access to selected properties of the field that it represents. It is returned by the getField function of uniface.Occurrence. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}